o the positive direction.</li>\r\n 	<li><em>Are you focused on what you want?</em> Focus, like a laser, is a gathering of energy that pinpoints one specific goal or purpose. It’s different from what you’ve been thinking about and how you interpret other’s actions, focus is where you want to ultimately be. Instead of focusing on things that you don’t want in your life, focus on what you do, and see how this alignment in energy shifts your propensity for success.</li>\r\n 	<li><em>What is it you want out of life?</em> By determining the answer to this question, you bring clarity into your life and start the process of making determined choices. Why do you want what you want? Once those questions are answered, it’s easier to see the path ahead, and how to go about getting to the success you see on the horizon.</li>\r\n</ul>','Raise Your Awareness and Boost Your Success with These Questions','','trash','open','open','','raise-your-awareness-and-boost-your-success-with-these-questions__trashed','','','2016-06-22 14:49:42','2016-06-22 14:49:42','',0,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/?p=1119',0,'post','',0),(1120,1,'2016-06-22 01:27:32','2016-06-22 01:27:32','Most people wander through life aimlessly, not sure of where they’re heading, or where they should even go next. The road to success, both personally and professionally, is paved with awareness, of living in the present, and being mindful of how you can grab hold of present day opportunities. Just as Rome wasn’t built in a day, success also takes time, and what better day than today to start on that journey. Ask yourself:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><em>What is it you’re thinking about?</em> Because thoughts turn into feelings, which then turn into behaviors. What you’re thinking determines how you will respond to various stimuli in your environment. If you think negatively, regardless of whether or not you should be (that client is calling me back because he’s upset with the product) for example, might hold a different reason altogether. Don’t make assumptions in your thoughts, give people the benefit of the doubt and find a reason to veer your thoughts into the positive direction.</li>\r\n 	<li><em>Are you focused on what you want?</em> Focus, like a laser, is a gathering of energy that pinpoints one specific goal or purpose. It’s different from what you’ve been thinking about and how you interpret other’s actions, focus is where you want to ultimately be. Instead of focusing on things that you don’t want in your life, focus on what you do, and see how this alignment in energy shifts your propensity for success.</li>\r\n 	<li><em>What is it you want out of life?</em> By determining the answer to this question, you bring clarity into your life and start the process of making determined choices. Why do you want what you want? Once those questions are answered, it’s easier to see the path ahead, and how to go about getting to the success you see on the horizon.</li>\r\n</ul>','Raise Your Awareness and Boost Your Success with These Questions','','inherit','closed','closed','','1119-revision-v1','','','2016-06-22 01:27:32','2016-06-22 01:27:32','',1119,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/2016/06/22/1119-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1137,1,'2016-06-22 12:24:34','2016-06-22 12:24:34',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1137','','','2016-06-23 13:30:23','2016-06-23 13:30:23','',0,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/?p=1137',14,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1141,1,'2016-06-22 12:29:07','2016-06-22 12:29:07','<h1>Understanding Our Process is Key to Success.</h1>\r\n<strong>At Vinehurst, we will sit down with you and discuss your goals and aspirations when it comes to selling your company. The following situations may apply to you:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Your company is growing and you need capital.</li>\r\n 	<li>Your company is growing and you need expertise to take it to the next level.,</li>\r\n 	<li>You would like to take some chips off the table.</li>\r\n 	<li>You need to retire and there are no family successors.</li>\r\n 	<li>There are family successors and they will need capital and/or expertise.</li>\r\n 	<li>You have been approached by your competition to sell your business.</li>\r\n 	<li>There is an industry consolidation happening.</li>\r\n 	<li>The marketplace is changing and you cannot or are not willing to invest to keep up.</li>\r\n 	<li>Your tired and want to do something else with your life.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLet Vinehurst assess your selling capabilities and see if you qualify for our representation.\r\n<h1>Review Your Selling Options.</h1>\r\n<strong>There are many options that you must take into strong consideration when selling. That includes:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Is it time to sell?</li>\r\n 	<li>Who are the buyers?</li>\r\n 	<li>Strategic or financial?</li>\r\n 	<li>Can I raise capital?</li>\r\n 	<li>Can or should I go public?</li>\r\n 	<li>Will I have to stay on and how long?</li>\r\n 	<li>What are Vinehurst\'s fees?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are their any upfront fees?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>The Valuation Process.</h1>\r\n<strong>At Vinehurst, the Valuation process is key. Important issues include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Should I pay for a valuation? How much?</li>\r\n 	<li>What multiple applies to my business?</li>\r\n 	<li>What methods or rules of thumb are used in our industry?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do assets matter?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do you apply gross sales</li>\r\n 	<li>What are the tax implications?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>Create A Strategic Plan, or Fail.</h1>\r\n<strong>Failing to create a plan will end up in failure. Important issues include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Which buyers do we approach first?</li>\r\n 	<li>How do we get the best price?</li>\r\n 	<li>How do we create completion for the deal?</li>\r\n 	<li>How do we keep it CONFIDENTIAL?</li>\r\n 	<li>Preparing the right marketing package</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>Marketing The Sale.</h1>\r\n<strong>Vinehurst markets our client\'s companies by using today\'s latest technology and social channels. Important issues include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The multifaceted approach. First strategic buyers, then financial, then open market.</li>\r\n 	<li>Create a bidding war.</li>\r\n 	<li>Qualify buyers</li>\r\n 	<li>Review their qualifications.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>Meet With Prospective Buyers.</h1>\r\n<strong>Vinehurst will screen potential buyers of your company via phone and email. Depending on the situation, we will also meet with them in person if deemed appropriate. Issues include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Meet with only the best buyers.</li>\r\n 	<li>How to handle conference calls.</li>\r\n 	<li>How to handle face-to-face meetings.</li>\r\n 	<li>Limited but important information.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>Solicit And Review Letters Of Intent (LOI’s).</h1>\r\n<strong>At Vinehurst, we work with you and your advisors to decide who is the best buyer. Important issues include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Who’s the best buyer?</li>\r\n 	<li>Cash, notes, earnouts, stock, escrow?</li>\r\n 	<li>Senior debt, mezzanine, secondary?</li>\r\n 	<li>No shops and non-solicitation agreements?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>Negotiate The Sale.</h1>\r\n<strong>Negotiating with Vinehurst always results in a higher selling price for our Clients. Important points include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Negotiation never ends.</li>\r\n 	<li>What should be in the LOI?</li>\r\n 	<li>When should the definitive agreements be drawn?</li>\r\n 	<li>How long for due diligence?</li>\r\n 	<li>Who pays the attorneys, CPA’s?</li>\r\n 	<li>Is an audit necessary?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>Due Diligence.</h1>\r\n<strong>Let Vinehurst manage the Due Diligence phase of the selling process. Important issues include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>What information is necessary?</li>\r\n 	<li>Where is due diligence done?</li>\r\n 	<li>What to do when the buyer asks you to cut out the intermediary, your attorney, or CPA?</li>\r\n 	<li>How not to get overwhelmed while the deal progresses</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>Close The Deal. Cash the Check.</h1>\r\n<strong>Once due diligence is over, then the M&amp;A process must be completed. Vinehurst will work tirelessly to get the transaction completed. Important issues include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Review and negotiate definitive agreements.</li>\r\n 	<li>Follow up with financing sources.</li>\r\n 	<li>Arrange real estate sales or lease transfers.</li>\r\n 	<li>Notify key employees at the appropriate time.</li>\r\n 	<li>Help arrange wire transfers.</li>\r\n 	<li>Make reservations for the celebratory dinner!!! (Perhaps even pick up the tab!)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis might seem like a lot of information, however, our job, our passion is making you, our Client feel comfortable as we embark together on the selling process of your business.\r\n\r\nFind out today if you qualify for our representation.','Selling Process','','publish','closed','closed','','selling-process','','','2016-06-23 13:15:27','2016-06-23 13:15:27','',0,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/?page_id=1141',0,'page','',0),(1134,1,'2016-06-22 12:05:07','2016-06-22 12:05:07',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1134','','','2016-06-23 13:30:23','2016-06-23 13:30:23','',0,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/?p=1134',7,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1135,1,'2016-06-22 12:05:07','2016-06-22 12:05:07',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1135','','','2016-06-23 13:30:23','2016-06-23 13:30:23','',0,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/?p=1135',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1136,1,'2016-06-22 12:05:07','2016-06-22 12:05:07',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1136','','','2016-06-23 13:30:23','2016-06-23 13:30:23','',0,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/?p=1136',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1371,1,'2016-06-23 13:26:20','2016-06-23 13:26:20','Our client has asked us to not provide a description of their business available for acquisition. Only financially qualified buyers may apply. Call Vinehurst today to learn more.','Sports Memorabilia Store','Our client has asked us to not provide a description of their business available for acquisition. Only financially