6-06-23 12:40:44','',0,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Vine-Hurst-Full.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1355,1,'2016-06-23 12:30:57','2016-06-23 12:30:57',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1355','','','2016-06-23 12:35:14','2016-06-23 12:35:14','',0,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/?p=1355',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1366,1,'2016-06-23 13:03:55','2016-06-23 13:03:55','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Who We Are</h3>\r\nVinehurst is an ultra exclusive brokerage boutique. 9 out of every 10 who apply to have Vinehurst represent their business sale are declined, based on our strict qualifying criteria.  We only represent clients who have operated a successful business and/or possess an amazing strategic acquisition. Vinehurst  has a strong foundation and global reach to close deals at all stages of the economic cycle. Our multi-sector know-how and worldwide connections make us ideally positioned to advise and guide clients on how to complete their transaction successfully, whatever the economic climate.\r\n\r\nAt Vinehurst, we advise public companies, family-owned businesses and private equity firms around the world on acquisitions, divestitures and fundraising on a local and global level.\r\n\r\nOur Firm closes hundreds of deals every year, giving us direct experience of businesses operating in every industry sector in countries around the world. We have advised on over 1000 transactions totaling more than US$3 billion in transaction value since 2000.\r\n\r\nBecause we live in a world of global markets that creates powerful merger and acquisition opportunities, all our advisors combine an international perspective with their local knowledge.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<b>Who We Help</b>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<b>Private Companies.</b>\r\n\r\nWe offer an advisory track record of unparalleled achievement for private and family businesses. Since 2009, we have advised on more than 200 transactions of this type in all major industry sectors. Our team of senior advisors led by Mr. Anderson, will guide you through the entire process to ensure confidentiality, efficiency and the best possible value for your business — with sensitivity, care and professionalism[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<b>Public Companies.</b>\r\n\r\nWe have assisted public companies on domestic and international M&amp;A transactions and fundraising for almost 14 years. We consistently achieve superior results by providing a team of senior\r\n\r\nprofessionals who offer unbiased advice, underpinned by decades of public sector experience. Our worldwide team of experts gives us the reach and resources to execute global acquisition programs, establish joint ventures or advise on the sale of subsidiaries to international buyers.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<b>Financial Professionals.</b>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nWe have unrivalled senior-level experience in advising private equity funds, family offices and institutional investors. Since 2010, we have advised over 80 financial investors on acquisitions, divestitures and fundraising efforts. We understand the features and characteristics of this industry, how its challenges influence our clients’ objectives and affect the measurements of success.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Exits — We can get a better exit for your investment by managing a competitive sales process that includes boutique and specialist buyers from around the world.</li>\r\n 	<li>Acquisitions — We can advise private equity funds and investors on building stronger portfolios and identifying add-ons to existing investments.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]At Vinehurst, we represent the world’s finest companies. To see if you qualify for our ultra exclusive representation, please call Mr. Anderson at <a href=\"tel:763-445-2669\" target=\"_blank\">763-445-2669</a>.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2016-06-23 13:03:55','2016-06-23 13:03:55','',2,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/2016/06/23/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1301,1,'2016-06-23 10:13:02','2016-06-23 10:13:02','','NextHome-Metro-Logo-Horizontal-small.Dark','','inherit','open','closed','','nexthome-metro-logo-horizontal-small-dark','','','2016-06-23 10:13:02','2016-06-23 10:13:02','',0,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/NextHome-Metro-Logo-Horizontal-small.Dark_.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1306,1,'2016-06-23 10:35:19','2016-06-23 10:35:19','','Home + Revolution Slider','','inherit','closed','closed','','275-revision-v1','','','2016-06-23 10:35:19','2016-06-23 10:35:19','',275,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/2016/06/23/275-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1312,1,'2016-06-23 10:39:43','2016-06-23 10:39:43','','Home + Revolution Slider','','inherit','closed','closed','','275-revision-v1','','','2016-06-23 10:39:43','2016-06-23 10:39:43','',275,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/2016/06/23/275-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1307,1,'2016-06-23 10:36:02','2016-06-23 10:36:02','[rev_slider alias=\"Home\"]','Home + Revolution Slider','','inherit','closed','closed','','275-revision-v1','','','2016-06-23 10:36:02','2016-06-23 10:36:02','',275,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/2016/06/23/275-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1308,1,'2016-06-23 10:37:07','2016-06-23 10:37:07','','Home + Revolution Slider','','inherit','closed','closed','','275-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-23 10:37:07','2016-06-23 10:37:07','',275,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/2016/06/23/275-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1311,1,'2016-06-23 10:39:22','2016-06-23 10:39:22','[rev_slider test]','Home + Revolution Slider','','inherit','closed','closed','','275-revision-v1','','','2016-06-23 10:39:22','2016-06-23 10:39:22','',275,'http://dev.vinehurst.com/2016/06/23/275-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1333,2,'2016-06-23 11:0